    <main>
      <section class="hero">
          <div class="hero-content">
              <h1>Save Life Donate<br>Stem Cells</h1>
              <p>Join us in the mission to save lives through stem cell donation. Your small contribution today could give someone a second chance at life tomorrow.</p>
