      <section class="mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We are dedicated to connecting stem cell donors with those in need, creating a global 
          network of hope and healing. Through education, support, and innovative matching 
          technology, we strive to make stem cell donation accessible and straightforward for 
          everyone who wishes to make a difference in someone's life.
        </p>
